Unlikely rap stars, important dumplings, feast etiquette: a smart guide to Georgia’s capital.

Drink wine out of repurposed Coca-Cola bottles. Georgia—a country of just under four million people on the Black Sea, straddling Eastern Europe and West Asia—claims to be the birthplace of wine.
